name: Cboe Europe B.V.
goal:
Cboe Europe B.V. operates a Regulated Market and a Multilateral Trading Facility as well as an Approved Publication Arrangement.
Cboe Europe B.V. is based in Amsterdam.

Cboe Europe B.V. obtained a license from the Dutch Ministry of Finance in March 2019.
interests: Banking and financial services, Competition, Economy, finance and the euro, Single market, Taxation
euInitiatives: Policies and legislation in relation to financial markets such as, but not limited to, Mifid 2, MAD/MAR, Benchmarks, EMIR, CMU and CSDR.
